{"tid":2108491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警 於靶場測試疑似發射器 未能損毀紙靶  辯方質疑小題大做","createTime":"2020-07-14T14:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T15:13:20.000Z","uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7025d5e0fd485ef3f55caa3f4ac661d76cca09e5","tid":2108491,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:43:05.000Z","msg":"控方下午傳召一名重案組警員，講述去年特意攜同涉案一個由膠水樽頸與汽球組合而成的疑似發射器，前往警察總部練靶場，在一米距離向一塊貼有紙張的木板拉動汽球内波子，以回彈方式向前發射。庭上播放片段可見，第一次發射未能令波子彈出，及後兩次成功發射，惟未能為紙靶做成任何損毀，只發出一聲撞擊聲音，測試至此完成。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：TMCC1653/19】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200713/TIXOPHTXOQCLFLSMCDDB6HGRIE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3pzG6fmv_oI54kg59JqleWWJXhBOUvjjYDlg0CjvnzbuxWrolhsHx6KVI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200713%2FTIXOPHTXOQCLFLSMCDDB6HGRIE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3pzG6fmv_oI54kg59JqleWWJXhBOUvjjYDlg0CjvnzbuxWrolhsHx6KVI&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=10b65dcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200713%2FTIXOPHTXOQCLFLSMCDDB6HGRIE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3pzG6fmv_oI54kg59JqleWWJXhBOUvjjYDlg0CjvnzbuxWrolhsHx6KVI&h=7f9dc97e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200713/TIXOPHTXOQCLFLSMCDDB6HGRIE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3pzG6fmv_oI54kg59JqleWWJXhBOUvjjYDlg0CjvnzbuxWrolhsHx6KVI</a>"},{"pid":"762e0e07933283967aa2a42ffe0a508917a33b98","tid":2108491,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},